# Telegram Bot Configuration
# 
# To enable Telegram reporting:
# 1. Create a new bot by messaging @BotFather on Telegram
# 2. Get your bot token from BotFather
# 3. Get your chat ID by messaging @userinfobot
# 4. Replace the values below and rename this file to .env
#
# Example:
# TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=1234567890:ABCdefGHIjklMNOpqrsTUVwxyz
# TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=123456789

TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=8334219975:AAFieeTvjCuupdaJ1s4fZqE5eviiYESo6yo
TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=8032328516
APP_SECRET=your-secret-key-here
NODE_ENV=production